comments: Porter Jr. (GSW) is firming up in Hampton's (ORL) path and absorbs the side to side contact during the screen.
Anthony (ORL) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Porter (GSW).
Porter Jr. (GSW) dives for the loose ball and makes contact to the ball with two hands without delivering contact to Anthony (ORL) prior to the correctly whistled jump ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) reaches in and makes contact to Green's (GSW) arm that affects his ability to pass.

The 24 second clock was erroneously reset to 10 seconds when it should have been a 24 second violation.  The shot clock should not reset because ORL never gained possession and the officials should of stopped play and given the ball to GS at 1:19 when they gained possession after the jump ball and reset the shot clock to 7.  Green gaining possession does not entitle them to a reset the clock as clip above shows GS with possession after a rebound in their front court led to the jump ball.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal contact with two hands to Hampton's (ORL) body as he clears space during the inbound.
Green (GSW) is losing possession of the ball when Green (GSW) reaches in and makes marginal contact to his body as he regains possession and makes the pass.
Anthony (ORL) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Bamba (ORL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Poole (GSW) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) makes contact to Wagner's (ORL) body and affects his shot attempt.  Replay review of the foul called on Thompson pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Thompson (GSW) makes some contact to Wagner's (ORL) arm as the timeout is called.
